nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A surreal fantasy glamour portrait of a woman with lavender skin and glowing silver tattoos across her forehead and temples. A spectral, ghost-white serpent with translucent scales wraps slowly from her jawline around her head like a crown. Its body reflects moonlight and starlight, almost ethereal. Her eyes are white with glowing irises, and her lips shimmer in pearlescent shades. Hair is long, silver, and floating around her as if suspended in water. The snake’s head rests gently on her brow, both of them staring forward as if in communion. Lighting is moonlight simulation with iridescent bounce. Background is a star-filled nebula. Mood is mystic, sacred, powerful. Color style is fantasy opalescent with cool glows and silvers.
